-- Magic Johnson Sells Stake in Los Angeles Lakers to Soon-Shiong, NBA Says
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2010-10-18T20:37:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/magic-johnson-sells-stake-in-los-angeles-lakers-to-soon-shiong-nba-says.html
Earvin “Magic” Johnson has sold
his stake in the Los Angeles Lakers to Patrick Soon-Shiong,
according to a statement on the team’s website.  Lakers majority owner Jerry Buss said the “sale of
Earvin’s share of the team is a business decision which will not
change our relationship. Our friendship goes well beyond
business. Patrick is a long-time and passionate Lakers fan and
we are delighted to have him as a partner.”  Details were not disclosed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  